**Status Legend:**
- ✅ **Done** - Completed and functional
- 🚧 **In Progress** - Currently being worked on
- ⏳ **Not Started** - Planned but not yet begun
- 📝 **Partial** - Partially complete, needs integration/completion
- 🔄 **Migrating** - Being migrated to Vue.js (Vue migration in progress)

