### Critical Path (MVP)

**Sequential Dependencies:**
1. **Feature 0** (Vue.js Migration) → Foundation (Phases 0.0-0.2 required for other features)
2. **Feature 1** (Core Infrastructure) → Depends on Feature 0 Phases 0.0-0.2
3. **Feature 2.0** (Jose's Wizard UI Port) → Depends on Feature 0 Phases 0.0-0.2 and Feature 1
4. **Feature 4** (API Integration) → Can develop in parallel (depends on Feature 1)
5. **Feature 2** (Customer Booking Wizard) → Depends on Feature 2.0 and Feature 4

**Parallel Work:**
- Feature 0 Phase 0.1 and 0.2 can run parallel (Data Layer and State Management)
- Feature 4 (API Integration) can run parallel with Feature 2.0 (UI Port) once Feature 0 Phases 0.0-0.2 complete
- Feature 3 (Admin Interface) conversion is Feature 0 Phase 0.4 (runs after Feature 0 Phase 0.2)
- Feature 4 API phases can run parallel (Phase 4.1, 4.2 independent; 4.3 depends on 4.2)

### Key Dependencies Map

```
Feature 0 (Vue.js Migration)
  ├─> No dependencies (foundational migration)
  │   ├─> Phase 0.0: Project Setup ✅
  │   ├─> Phase 0.1: Data Layer Foundation 🚧
  │   ├─> Phase 0.2: State Management 🚧
  │   ├─> Phase 0.3: Property System Refactor ⏳
  │   ├─> Phase 0.4: Admin Wizard ⏳ (Feature 3 conversion)
  │   ├─> Phase 0.5: Scheduler Wizard ⏳ (Feature 2.0 conversion)
  │   └─> Phase 0.6: React Cleanup ⏳ (final cleanup)
  │
Feature 1 (Core Infrastructure)
  └─> Depends on: Feature 0 Phases 0.0-0.2
  │
Feature 2.0 (Jose's Wizard UI Port)
  ├─> Depends on: Feature 0 Phases 0.0-0.2
  └─> Depends on: Feature 1
  │
Feature 2 (Customer Booking Wizard)
  ├─> Depends on: Feature 1
  ├─> Depends on: Feature 2.0 (UI port must complete first)
  └─> Depends on: Feature 4 (API Integration Layer)
  │
Feature 3 (Admin Configuration Interface)
  ├─> Depends on: Feature 1
  └─> Depends on: Feature 0 Phase 0.4 (Vue conversion)
  │
Feature 4 (API Integration Layer)
  └─> Depends on: Feature 1
```

