    F20 --> F2[Feature 2: Customer Booking Wizard]
    F4 --> F2
    
    F2 --> F5[Feature 5: Future Features]
    F3 --> F5
    
    style F1 fill:#90EE90
    style F20 fill:#FFE4B5
    style F2 fill:#87CEEB
    style F4 fill:#DDA0DD
    style F3 fill:#F0E68C
    style F5 fill:#D3D3D3
```

**Legend:**
- 🟢 Green: Foundational (no dependencies)
- 🟡 Yellow: UI Port (depends on foundation)
- 🔵 Blue: Core MVP Feature
- 🟣 Purple: Infrastructure Layer
- 🟨 Yellow: Admin Feature
- ⚪ Gray: Post-MVP

### Dependency Map

```
Feature 1: Core Infrastructure
  └─> No dependencies (foundational)

Feature 2.0: Jose's Wizard UI Port
  ├─> Depends on: Feature 1 (Core Infrastructure)
  └─> Depends on: Feature 0 Phases 0.0-0.2 (Vuexy setup, Pinia stores)

Feature 2: Customer Booking Wizard
  ├─> Depends on: Feature 1 (Core Infrastructure)
  ├─> Depends on: Feature 2.0 (Jose's Wizard UI Port) - Must complete UI port first
  └─> Depends on: Feature 4 (API Integration Layer) - For Google Calendar, Maps, MLS APIs

Feature 3: Admin Configuration Interface
  └─> Depends on: Feature 1 (Core Infrastructure)
  └─> Depends on: Feature 0 Phase 0.4 (being converted from React)

Feature 4: API Integration Layer (Infrastructure)
  └─> Depends on: Feature 1 (Core Infrastructure)
  └─> Note: Provides infrastructure; actual integration happens in Feature 2 phases

Feature 5: Future Features Catalog
  └─> Depends on: Features 1-4 (Core functionality)
```

### Critical Path (MVP)

**MVP Critical Path:**
1. **Feature 0** (Vue.js Migration) - Foundation (Phases 0.0-0.2 must complete first)
2. **Feature 1** (Core Infrastructure) - Depends on Feature 0 Phases 0.0-0.2
3. **Feature 2.0** (Jose's Wizard UI Port) - Depends on Feature 0 Phases 0.0-0.2 and Feature 1
4. **Feature 4** (API Integration Layer) - Can be developed in parallel (depends on Feature 1)
5. **Feature 2** (Customer Booking Wizard) - Depends on Feature 2.0 and Feature 4
   - Phase 2.2 depends on Feature 4 (Google Maps API - MVP-critical)
   - Phase 2.3 depends on Feature 4 (Google Calendar API - MVP-critical)
   - Phase 2.5 depends on Feature 4 (Google Calendar API event creation - MVP-critical)

**Parallel Work Opportunities:**
- Feature 4 (API Integration) can be developed in parallel with Feature 2.0 (UI Port)
- Feature 3 (Admin Interface) conversion is Feature 0 Phase 0.4 (runs after Feature 0 Phase 0.2)
- Feature 4 API phases can be developed in parallel (Phase 4.1, 4.2 independent; 4.3 depends on 4.2)

### Phase Dependencies Within Features

#### Feature 2.0 Dependencies
- Phase 2.0.1 → Phase 2.0.2 → Phase 2.0.3 → Phase 2.0.4 → Phase 2.0.5 → Phase 2.0.6 (sequential)
- All phases depend on Feature 0 Phases 0.0-0.2

#### Feature 2 Dependencies
- Phase 2.1 → Phase 2.2 → Phase 2.3 → Phase 2.4 → Phase 2.5 (sequential)
- Phase 2.1 depends on Feature 2.0 Phase 2.0.2 (Step 1 UI port)
- Phase 2.2 depends on Feature 2.0 Phase 2.0.3 (Step 2 UI port) and Feature 4 (Google Maps API)
- Phase 2.3 depends on Feature 2.0 Phase 2.0.4 (Step 3 UI port) and Feature 4 (Google Calendar API)
- Phase 2.4 depends on Feature 2.0 Phase 2.0.5 (Step 4 UI port)
- Phase 2.5 depends on Feature 2.0 Phase 2.0.6 (Step 5 UI port) and Feature 4 (Google Calendar API event creation)

#### Feature 4 Dependencies
- Phase 4.1, 4.2 can be developed in parallel (independent APIs)
- Phase 4.3 depends on Phase 4.2 (MLS uses address from Maps)

#### Feature 3 Dependencies
- Phase 3.1 → Phase 3.2 → Phase 3.3 (sequential, but can overlap)
- All phases depend on Feature 1 and Feature 0 Phase 0.4

