## Document Structure Notes

This document follows a 4-tier architecture pattern:
- **Features** (Tier 1) - Major initiatives spanning multiple phases
- **Phases** (Tier 2) - Major milestones within features
- **Sessions** (Tier 3) - Focused work within phases
- **Tasks** (Tier 4) - Single focused work items

**Navigation:**
- Use the [Table of Contents](#table-of-contents) at the top for quick navigation
- Use the [Master Feature Index](#master-feature-index) for status overview and quick links
- Each feature section contains complete details including phases, sessions, and tasks

**Future Structure:**
- This document may be split into separate feature guides in `.cursor/project-manager/features/dhp-differential-scheduler/` when ready
- Current structure keeps all planning in one document for easy reference

